START: Hostel register 
Enter user type(front end/hostel end)
IF (user type is front end)
THEN enter the enrollment number
    IF (The enrollment number is in database)
    THEN input the destination 
    Add record to the data base(enrollment number, destination, time)
    Display successfully updated
    ELSE Display invalid number
    ENDIF
ELSE (user end is hostel)
Select hostel 
Store hostel name
 IF (check new record on database)
 Get enrollment number 
 Fetch student's details from students's database
  IF(hostel A)
  Display sign out details to A
  ELSE Display sign out details to B

ENDIF
